{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.1","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 34:1","prev_osis_id":"Gen.033.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.034.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Dina et les Sich\u00e9mites<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-31: cf. 1 Co 15:33. De 22:28, 29. Pr 26:24-26. Ge 49:5-7.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.34.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>\n    Dina, la fille que L\u00e9a avait enfant\u00e9e \u00e0 Jacob, sortit pour voir les filles du pays.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.34","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.2","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:2","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.33.20","name":"Gen\u00e8se 33:20","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.33.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.2","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 34:2","prev_osis_id":"Gen.034.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.034.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.34.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Elle fut aper\u00e7ue de Sichem, fils de Hamor, prince du pays. Il l\u2019enleva, coucha avec elle, et la d\u00e9shonora.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.34","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.3","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:3","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.1","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:1","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.3","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 34:3","prev_osis_id":"Gen.034.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.034.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.34.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Son c\u0153ur s\u2019attacha \u00e0 Dina, fille de Jacob; il aima la jeune fille, et sut parler \u00e0 son c\u0153ur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.34","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.4","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:4","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.2","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:2","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.4","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 34:4","prev_osis_id":"Gen.034.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.034.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.34.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Et Sichem dit \u00e0 Hamor, son p\u00e8re: Donne-moi cette jeune fille pour femme.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.34","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.5","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:5","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.3","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:3","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.5","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 34:5","prev_osis_id":"Gen.034.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.034.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.34.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Jacob apprit qu\u2019il avait d\u00e9shonor\u00e9 Dina, sa fille; et, comme ses fils \u00e9taient aux champs avec son troupeau, Jacob garda le silence jusqu\u2019\u00e0 leur retour.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.34","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.6","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:6","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.4","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:4","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.6","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 34:6","prev_osis_id":"Gen.034.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.034.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.34.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Hamor, p\u00e8re de Sichem, se rendit aupr\u00e8s de Jacob pour lui parler.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.34","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.7","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:7","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.5","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:5","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.7","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 34:7","prev_osis_id":"Gen.034.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.034.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.34.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Et les fils de Jacob revenaient des champs, lorsqu\u2019ils apprirent la chose; ces hommes furent irrit\u00e9s et se mirent dans une grande col\u00e8re, parce que Sichem avait commis une infamie en Isra\u00ebl, en couchant avec la fille de Jacob, ce qui n\u2019aurait pas d\u00fb se faire.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.34","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.8","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:8","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.6","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:6","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.8","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 34:8","prev_osis_id":"Gen.034.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.034.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.34.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Hamor leur adressa ainsi la parole: Le c\u0153ur de Sichem, mon fils, s\u2019est attach\u00e9 \u00e0 votre fille; donnez-la-lui pour femme, je vous prie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.34","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.9","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:9","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.7","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:7","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.9","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 34:9","prev_osis_id":"Gen.034.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.034.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.34.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Alliez-vous avec nous; vous nous donnerez vos filles, et vous prendrez pour vous les n\u00f4tres.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.34","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.10","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:10","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.8","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:8","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.10","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 34:10","prev_osis_id":"Gen.034.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.034.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.34.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Vous habiterez avec nous, et le pays sera \u00e0 votre disposition; restez, pour y trafiquer et y acqu\u00e9rir des propri\u00e9t\u00e9s.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.34","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.11","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:11","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.9","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:9","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.11","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 34:11","prev_osis_id":"Gen.034.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.034.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.34.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Sichem dit au p\u00e8re et aux fr\u00e8res de Dina: Que je trouve gr\u00e2ce \u00e0 vos yeux, et je donnerai ce que vous me direz.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.34","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.12","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:12","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.10","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:10","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.12","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 34:12","prev_osis_id":"Gen.034.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.034.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.34.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Exigez de moi une forte dot et beaucoup de pr\u00e9sents, et je donnerai ce que vous me direz; mais accordez-moi pour femme la jeune fille.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.34","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.13","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:13","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.11","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:11","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.13","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 34:13","prev_osis_id":"Gen.034.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.034.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.34.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Les fils de Jacob r\u00e9pondirent et parl\u00e8rent avec ruse \u00e0 Sichem et \u00e0 Hamor, son p\u00e8re, parce que Sichem avait d\u00e9shonor\u00e9 Dina, leur s\u0153ur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.34","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.14","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:14","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.12","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:12","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.14","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 34:14","prev_osis_id":"Gen.034.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.034.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.34.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Ils leur dirent: C\u2019est une chose que nous ne pouvons pas faire, que de donner notre s\u0153ur \u00e0 un homme incirconcis; car ce serait un opprobre pour nous.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.34","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.15","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:15","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.13","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:13","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.15","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 34:15","prev_osis_id":"Gen.034.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.034.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.34.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Nous ne consentirons \u00e0 votre d\u00e9sir qu\u2019\u00e0 la condition que vous deveniez comme nous, et que tout m\u00e2le parmi vous soit circoncis.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.34","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.16","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:16","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.14","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:14","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.16","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 34:16","prev_osis_id":"Gen.034.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.034.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.34.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Nous vous donnerons alors nos filles, et nous prendrons pour nous les v\u00f4tres; nous habiterons avec vous, et nous formerons un seul peuple.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.34","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.17","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:17","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.15","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:15","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.17","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 34:17","prev_osis_id":"Gen.034.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.034.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.34.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Mais si vous ne voulez pas nous \u00e9couter et vous faire circoncire, nous prendrons notre fille, et nous nous en irons.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.34","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.18","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:18","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.16","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:16","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.18","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 34:18","prev_osis_id":"Gen.034.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.034.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.34.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Leurs paroles eurent l\u2019assentiment de Hamor et de Sichem, fils de Hamor.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.34","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.19","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:19","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.17","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:17","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.19","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 34:19","prev_osis_id":"Gen.034.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.034.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.34.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Le jeune homme ne tarda pas \u00e0 faire la chose, car il aimait la fille de Jacob. Il \u00e9tait consid\u00e9r\u00e9 de tous dans la maison de son p\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.34","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.20","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:20","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.18","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:18","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.20","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 34:20","prev_osis_id":"Gen.034.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.034.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.34.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Hamor et Sichem, son fils, se rendirent \u00e0 la porte de leur ville, et ils parl\u00e8rent ainsi aux gens de leur ville:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.34","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.21","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:21","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.19","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:19","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.21","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 34:21","prev_osis_id":"Gen.034.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.034.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.34.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Ces hommes sont paisibles \u00e0 notre \u00e9gard; qu\u2019ils restent dans le pays, et qu\u2019ils y trafiquent; le pays est assez vaste pour eux. Nous prendrons pour femmes leurs filles, et nous leur donnerons nos filles.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.34","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.22","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:22","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.20","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:20","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.22","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 34:22","prev_osis_id":"Gen.034.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.034.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.34.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Mais ces hommes ne consentiront \u00e0 habiter avec nous, pour former un seul peuple, qu\u2019\u00e0 la condition que tout m\u00e2le parmi nous soit circoncis, comme ils sont eux-m\u00eames circoncis.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.34","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.23","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:23","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.21","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:21","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.23","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 34:23","prev_osis_id":"Gen.034.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.034.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.34.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Leurs troupeaux, leurs biens et tout leur b\u00e9tail, ne seront-ils pas \u00e0 nous? Acceptons seulement leur condition, pour qu\u2019ils restent avec nous.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.34","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.24","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:24","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.22","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:22","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.24","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 34:24","prev_osis_id":"Gen.034.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.034.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.34.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Tous ceux qui \u00e9taient venus \u00e0 la porte de la ville \u00e9cout\u00e8rent Hamor et Sichem, son fils; et tous les m\u00e2les se firent circoncire, tous ceux qui \u00e9taient venus \u00e0 la porte de la ville.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.34","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.25","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:25","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.23","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:23","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.25","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 34:25","prev_osis_id":"Gen.034.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.034.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.34.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Le troisi\u00e8me jour, pendant qu\u2019ils \u00e9taient souffrants, les deux fils de Jacob, Sim\u00e9on et L\u00e9vi, fr\u00e8res de Dina, prirent chacun leur \u00e9p\u00e9e, tomb\u00e8rent sur la ville qui se croyait en s\u00e9curit\u00e9, et tu\u00e8rent tous les m\u00e2les.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.34","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.26","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:26","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.24","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:24","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.26","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 34:26","prev_osis_id":"Gen.034.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.034.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.34.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Ils pass\u00e8rent aussi au fil de l\u2019\u00e9p\u00e9e Hamor et Sichem, son fils; ils enlev\u00e8rent Dina de la maison de Sichem, et sortirent.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.34","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.27","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:27","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.25","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:25","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.27","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 34:27","prev_osis_id":"Gen.034.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.034.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.34.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>Les fils de Jacob se jet\u00e8rent sur les morts, et pill\u00e8rent la ville, parce qu\u2019on avait d\u00e9shonor\u00e9 leur s\u0153ur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.34","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.28","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:28","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.26","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:26","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.28","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 34:28","prev_osis_id":"Gen.034.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.034.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.34.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Ils prirent leurs troupeaux, leurs b\u0153ufs et leurs \u00e2nes, ce qui \u00e9tait dans la ville et ce qui \u00e9tait dans les champs;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.34","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.29","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:29","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.27","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:27","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.29","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 34:29","prev_osis_id":"Gen.034.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.034.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.34.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>ils emmen\u00e8rent comme butin toutes leurs richesses, leurs enfants et leurs femmes, et tout ce qui se trouvait dans les maisons.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.34","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.30","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:30","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.28","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:28","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.30","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 34:30","prev_osis_id":"Gen.034.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.034.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.34.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>Alors Jacob dit \u00e0 Sim\u00e9on et \u00e0 L\u00e9vi: Vous me troublez, en me rendant odieux aux habitants du pays, aux Canan\u00e9ens et aux Ph\u00e9r\u00e9siens. Je n\u2019ai qu\u2019un petit nombre d\u2019hommes; et ils se rassembleront contre moi, ils me frapperont, et je serai d\u00e9truit, moi et ma maison.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.34","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.31","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:31","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.29","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:29","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.31","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 34:31","prev_osis_id":"Gen.034.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.035.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.34.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>Ils r\u00e9pondirent: Traitera-t-on notre s\u0153ur comme une prostitu\u00e9e?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.34","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.35.1","name":"Gen\u00e8se 35:1","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.35.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.34.30","name":"Gen\u00e8se 34:30","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.34.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81e76e2ca01.46784677');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81e76e2ca01.46784677\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81e76e2ca01.46784677","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81e76e2ca01.46784677'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81e76e2ca01.46784677\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}